name: Mysteries of incarnation
description: This picture is about deep transcendental processes, mysteries from Cosmism to the core of the Earth. From our roots, elements to the Higher Self, superconsciousness. Occurring both inside and outside of our consciousness, through the opening of the heart.  The genetic code that carries the wisdom of Oneness, generates multiplicity. As Isis, personifying wisdom and motherhood, fertile new life. Incarnating Eternity.
